u0111\u1ed9ng 4G l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\&quot;&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. B\u1ed9 ph\u00e1t wifi 4G c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec7n \u00edch v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i&lt;\/strong&gt;&lt;\/h2&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Nh\u1edd c\u00f3 b\u1ed9 ph\u00e1t wifi 4G m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Internet b\u1ea5t k\u00ec l\u00fac n\u00e0o b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y vi\u1ec7c xem phim, l\u01b0\u1edbt web c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u1edf kh\u1eafp m\u1ecdi n\u01a1i.&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;div class=\&quot;image\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https:\/\/hegka.com\/storage\/image-content\/aYcVrx9QPf1uS2xLWsMjXXj6N0ZqqQ4q4cQJBRLm6znwz.jpg\&quot; alt=\&quot;B\u1ed9 ph\u00e1t wifi 4G c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec7n \u00edch v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i\&quot;&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u00ednh n\u0103ng \u01b0u vi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 sau:&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Si\u00eau t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9: T\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 4G cao g\u1ea5p 10 l\u1ea7n so v\u1edbi 3G (150Mbps).&lt;\/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 theo th\u1eddi gian th\u1ef1c: 4G gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ebfn 2,5 l\u1ea7n so v\u1edbi 3G. Gi\u1ea3m h\u1eb3n hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ping cao, lag m\u1ea1ng.&lt;\/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Livestream, xem video, xem phim v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c m\u01b0\u1ee3t, full HD kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eadt lag.&lt;\/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;T\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea3i xu\u1ed1ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng: T\u1ea3i b\u00e0i h\u00e1t (dung l\u01b0\u1ee3ng 10MB): ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 1 gi\u00e2y v\u1edbi 4G (trong khi 3G c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea7n 10s). M\u1edf m\u1ed9t trang website: Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 3 gi\u00e2y v\u1edbi 4G (trong khi 3G c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea7n 9 gi\u00e2y.&lt;\/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;T\u1ea3i game (dung l\u01b0\u1ee3ng 20MB) ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 25 gi\u00e2y v\u1edbi 4G (trong khi 3G c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t 3 ph\u00fat). \u0110\u0103ng t\u1ea3i \u1ea3nh l\u00ean Facebook, Instagram ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 1 gi\u00e2y v\u1edbi 4G (trong khi 3G c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 25 gi\u00e2y)&lt;\/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u1ed9 ph\u00e1t wifi 4G c\u00f2n c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng l\u00e0m s\u1ea1c d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng cho \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i, m\u00e1y t\u00ednh b\u1ea3ng,\u2026&lt;\/li&gt;\n&lt;\/ul&gt;\n&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3. C\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd g\u00ec khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b\u1ed9 ph\u00e1t wifi 4G?&lt;\/strong&gt;&lt;\/h2&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;C\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b\u1ed9 ph\u00e1t wifi 3G\/4G th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?&lt;\/strong&gt;&lt;\/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 t\u1eebng h\u00e3ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c nhau, nh\u01b0ng nh\u00ec chung c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b\u1ed9 ph\u00e1t wifi 3G\/4G h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. B\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 vi\u1ec7c th\u00e1o n\u1eafp l\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb, g\u1eafn sim 4G v\u00e0o khe sim. Sau \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1ea5n gi\u1eef n\u00fat ngu\u1ed3n trong v\u00e0i gi\u00e2y cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh b\u1eadt s\u00e1ng. Khi c\u00f3 hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb t\u00ean nh\u00e0 m\u1ea1ng, c\u1ed9t s\u00f3ng 4G l\u00e0 thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\u00a0&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;div class=\&quot;image\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https:\/\/hegka.com\/storage\/image-content\/ESxXsr6tUVDdW9TOoKJ2KUa9Nf1SJc6HEeb3dGLrh6ayI.jpg\&quot; alt=\&quot;C\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b\u1ed9 ph\u00e1t wifi 3G\/4G th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?\&quot;&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;C\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1eadt kh\u1ea9u b\u1ed9 ph\u00e1t wifi sim 4G \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng?&lt;\/strong&gt;&lt;\/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;B\u1ea1n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00ean, m\u1eadt kh\u1ea9u cho wifi 4G t\u1eeb b\u1ed9 ph\u00e1t wifi \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u00ednh b\u1ea3o m\u1eadt, chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng.&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;N\u1ebfu sim 4G h\u1ebft dung l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a th\u00ec sao?&lt;\/strong&gt;&lt;\/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;C\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ea1ng 3G, 4G tr\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i, n\u1ebfu h\u1ebft dung l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a th\u00ec t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u00e1t ra s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 2G.&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;div class=\&quot;image\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https:\/\/hegka.com\/storage\/image-content\/Aw2MXyee9RLqL9wsRjBSgk9fkI6LzcdFSBv6Ih02jQT5G.jpg\&quot; alt=\&quot;N\u1ebfu sim 4G h\u1ebft dung l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a th\u00ec sao?\&quot;&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;C\u00f3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed9 ph\u00e1t wifi 3G\/4G \u1edf mi\u1ec1n n\u00fai, v\u00f9ng s\u00e2u v\u00f9ng xa kh\u00f4ng?&lt;\/strong&gt;&lt;\/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;V\u00ec c\u01a1 s\u1edf h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng c\u1ee7a mi\u1ec1n n\u00fai, v\u00f9ng s\u00e2u ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b\u1ed9 ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng wifi t\u1eeb sim 4G\/3G s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u, t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u kh\u00f4ng \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, ch\u1eadp ch\u1eddn.&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng sim 4G t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 m\u1ea1ng n\u00e0o?&lt;\/strong&gt;&lt;\/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;H\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i b\u1ed9 ph\u00e1t wifi 3G\/4G c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng hi\u1ec7n n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00edch v\u1edbi c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 m\u1ea1ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng sim 4G c\u1ee7a Viettel, Vinaphone, Mobifone, Vietnamobile,\u2026\u00a0&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;4. L\u1eddi k\u1ebft&lt;\/strong&gt;&lt;\/h2&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch b\u1ed9 ph\u00e1t wifi di \u0111\u1ed9ng 4G l\u00e0 g\u00ec? C\u00f3 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft hay kh\u00f4ng? Nh\u1eefng l\u01b0u \u00fd khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng? V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean, mong r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea1n hi\u1ec3u h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb ti\u1ec7n \u00edch n\u00e0y v\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.&lt;\/p&gt;\n&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;Khi nhu c\u1ea7u truy c\u1eadp Internet m\u1ecdi l\u00fac m\u1ecdi n\u01a1i t\u0103ng cao, nhu c\u1ea7u s\u1ef1 d\u1ee5ng m\u1ea1ng 4G nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, b\u1ed9 ph\u00e1t wifi di \u0111\u1ed9ng 4G ra \u0111\u1eddi. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft b\u1ed9 ph\u00e1t wifi di \u0111\u1ed9ng 4G l\u00e0 g\u00ec? C\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd g\u00ec khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng hay kh\u00f4ng? H\u00e3y theo d\u00f5i ngay b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y nh\u00e9!&quot;,&quot;thumb_image&quot;:null,&quot;tags&quot;:[&quot;B\u1ed9 ph\u00e1t wifi di \u0111\u1ed9ng 4G l\u00e0 g\u00ec?&quot;],&quot;slug&quot;:&quot;bo-phat-wifi-di-dong-4g-la-gi-co-thuc-su-tien-dung&quot;,&quot;content_share&quot;:null,&quot;image&quot;:&quot;articles\/05-2022\/62Ew2XUF7tqR2UNN1KAsdtTzNNJLwFSMBFNmCbfO.jpg&quot;,&quot;like&quot;:0,&quot;love&quot;:0,&quot;haha&quot;:0,&quot;wow&quot;:0,&quot;cry&quot;:0,&quot;angry&quot;:0,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;public&quot;,&quot;group_id&quot;:3,&quot;is_active&quot;:1,&quot;created_by&quot;:&quot;USER: #51&quot;,&quot;updated_by&quot;:&quot;ADMIN: #0&quot;,&quot;deleted_by&quot;:null,&quot;created_at&quot;:&quot;2022-05-03T16:57:54.000000Z&quot;,&quot;updated_at&quot;:&quot;2022-05-03T16:57:56.000000Z&quot;,&quot;deleted_at&quot;:null,&quot;parent_id&quot;:null,&quot;user_id&quot;:51,&quot;comment_count&quot;:0,&quot;url&quot;:null,&quot;is_post&quot;:1,&quot;vote&quot;:0,&quot;vote_up&quot;:null,&quot;vote_down&quot;:null,&quot;extension&quot;:&quot;jpg&quot;,&quot;host_share&quot;:null,&quot;link_share&quot;:null,&quot;image_share&quot;:null,&quot;title_share&quot;:null,&quot;reaction&quot;:0,&quot;heart_count&quot;:0,&quot;heart&quot;:null,&quot;width&quot;:0,&quot;height&quot;:0,&quot;ratio&quot;:1,&quot;content_150&quot;:&quot;&lt;p&gt;Khi nhu c\u1ea7u truy c\u1eadp Internet m\u1ecdi l\u00fac m\u1ecdi n\u01a1i t\u0103ng cao, nhu c\u1ea7u s\u1ef1 d\u1ee5ng m\u1ea1ng 4G nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, b\u1ed9 ph\u00e1t wifi di \u0111\u1ed9ng 4G ra \u0111\u1eddi. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft b\u1ed9 ph...&lt;\/p&gt;&quot;,&quot;content_250&quot;:&quot;&lt;p&gt;Khi nhu c\u1ea7u truy c\u1eadp Internet m\u1ecdi l\u00fac m\u1ecdi n\u01a1i t\u0103ng cao, nhu c\u1ea7u s\u1ef1 d\u1ee5ng m\u1ea1ng 4G nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, b\u1ed9 ph\u00e1t wifi di \u0111\u1ed9ng 4G ra \u0111\u1eddi. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft b\u1ed9 ph\u00e1t wifi di \u0111\u1ed9ng 4G l\u00e0 g\u00ec? C\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd g\u00ec khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng hay kh\u00f4ng? H\u00e3y theo d\u00f5i ngay b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y nh\u00e9!1. ...&lt;\/p&gt;&quot;,&quot;image_url&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/hegka.com\/storage\/articles\/05-2022\/62Ew2XUF7tqR2UNN1KAsdtTzNNJLwFSMBFNmCbfO.jpg&quot;,&quot;image_urls&quot;:[],&quot;vote_type&quot;:0},{&quot;id&quot;:1582,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Internet tivi l\u00e0 g\u00ec? Nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng th\u00fa v\u1ecb b\u1ea1n ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft&quot;,&quot;content&quot;:&quot;&lt;p&gt;C\u00e1c d\u00f2ng tivi hi\u1ec7n nay \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 nhu c\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng cao c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng. Internet tivi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ed9 gia \u0111\u00ecnh. V\u1eady Internet tivi l\u00e0 g\u00ec? C\u00f9ng m\u00ecnh kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 ngay nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng th\u00fa v\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Internet tivi trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft sau nh\u00e9!&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1. Internet tivi l\u00e0 g\u00ec?&lt;\/strong&gt;&lt;\/h2&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Internet tivi l\u00e0 d\u00f2ng tivi c\u00f3&lt;strong&gt;\u00a0kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i Internet.&lt;\/strong&gt; Nh\u1edd v\u1eady, tivi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng\u00a0&lt;strong&gt; &lt;\/strong&gt;\u0111\u1ec3 xem phim, \u0111\u1ecdc b\u00e1o, l\u01b0\u1edbt web b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng. Ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c k\u1ebft n\u1ed1t b\u1eb1ng WiFi, Tivi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 truy c\u1eadp Internet nh\u1edd c\u1ed5ng LAN. Hi\u1ec7n nay, nhi\u1ec1u th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e3 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t Internet Tivi t\u1eeb Sony, Samsung, t\u1edbi LG\u2026 v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 gi\u00e1 th\u00e0nh h\u1ee3p t\u00fai ti\u1ec1n.&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;div class=\&quot;image\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https:\/\/hegka.com\/storage\/image-content\/jIai1kDHABdgJZf7OyVnK4PJogtswTUWkp4TDG26IuELd.jpg\&quot; alt=\&quot; Internet tivi l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\&quot;&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1i Internet tivi n\u00e0o?&lt;\/strong&gt;&lt;\/h2&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng hi\u1ec7n nay c\u00f3 hai lo\u1ea1i tivi nh\u01b0 sau:&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Internet tivi c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n&lt;\/strong&gt;&lt;\/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u00f2ng tivi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3&lt;strong&gt;\u00a0&lt;\/strong&gt;truy c\u1eadp Internet \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ecdc b\u00e1o, l\u01b0\u1edbt web,\u2026 Tuy nhi\u00ean, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3\u00a0&lt;strong&gt;s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng s\u1eb5n c\u00f3 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng kh\u00e1c&lt;\/strong&gt;.&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;div class=\&quot;image\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https:\/\/hegka.com\/storage\/image-content\/u6yQ11O1QDZWiiyUJZG4ZCLo5DLBpglJ1gLEUIFfKywgk.jpg\&quot; alt=\&quot;Internet tivi c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n\&quot;&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Internet tivi c\u00f3 h\u1ec7 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh\u00a0&lt;\/strong&gt;&lt;\/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u01a1n, d\u00f2ng tivi n\u00e0y ch\u1ea1y h\u1ec7 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh, giao di\u1ec7n kh\u1ee7ng nh\u01b0 Smart Tivi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, tivi s\u1ebd s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng v\u00e0 kho \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i v\u00e0 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng h\u01a1n Internet tivi&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;div class=\&quot;image\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https:\/\/hegka.com\/storage\/image-content\/3Sm3FR4ndXE6HvbKPPGqZqVArTLov71BrRMLr8OlL2PmV.jpg\&quot; alt=\&quot;Internet tivi c\u00f3 h\u1ec7 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh \&quot;&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3. Kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 t\u00ednh n\u0103ng th\u00fa v\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Internet Tivi&lt;\/strong&gt;&lt;\/h2&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3\u00a0&lt;strong&gt;xem ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u1ecdi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m&lt;\/strong&gt;\u00a0m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00e0i truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y n\u1eefa. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng coi l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp phim \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u00ean Internet. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed s\u1ebd \u0111a d\u1ea1ng h\u01a1n nh\u1edd kho phim kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3.&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;div class=\&quot;image\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https:\/\/hegka.com\/storage\/image-content\/2S5HgiUskOFbmbfTlwoRUeU5w9zVdtNESgJohncq4e9wq.jpg\&quot; alt=\&quot;t\u00ednh n\u0103ng th\u00fa v\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Internet Tivi\&quot;&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Ngo\u00e0i ra,\u00a0Internet tivi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c\u00a0&lt;strong&gt;trang b\u1ecb c\u1ed5ng k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i LAN v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i Wi-Fi&lt;\/strong&gt;\u00a0n\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng truy c\u1eadp v\u00e0o Internet th\u1ecfa th\u00edch kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 kho \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n.&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;div class=\&quot;image\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https:\/\/hegka.com\/storage\/image-content\/z2SyGEYsLol5qlTjkY0kvzIgD6LJkrfcQTzhd1IX34fsv.jpg\&quot; alt=\&quot;Kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 t\u00ednh n\u0103ng th\u00fa v\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Internet Tivi\&quot;&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;4. Internet Tivi c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m g\u00ec?&lt;\/strong&gt;&lt;\/h2&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u01b0u v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Internet tivi m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n n\u00ean bi\u1ebft nh\u01b0 sau:&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m:&lt;\/strong&gt;&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;D\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i Internet \u0111\u1ec3 l\u01b0\u1edbt web, \u0111\u1ecdc b\u00e1o&lt;\/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Truy c\u1eadp v\u00e0o kho phim, video kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a Youtube v\u00e0 Netflix,\u2026&lt;\/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;D\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n v\u00e0 ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m th\u1eddi gian v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfc\u00a0remote.&lt;\/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;\u0110a d\u1ea1ng v\u1ec1 m\u1eabu m\u00e3 v\u00e0 gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3.&lt;\/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;N\u1ed9i dung gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed phong ph\u00fa.&lt;\/li&gt;\n&lt;\/ul&gt;\n&lt;div class=\&quot;image\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https:\/\/hegka.com\/storage\/image-content\/lT0ET0bSgJoD9tx0tYMUwVGaRVPKs3xrKt8xUshv64KWb.jpg\&quot; alt=\&quot;\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Internet Tivi\&quot;&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m:&lt;\/strong&gt;&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Tivi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb b\u1ed9 nh\u1edb trong, b\u1ed9 nh\u1edb RAM&lt;\/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Kho \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n. H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t th\u00eam \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng&lt;\/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n b\u1eb1ng khu\u00f4n m\u1eb7t, gi\u1ecdng n\u00f3i.&lt;\/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 giao di\u1ec7n th\u00f4ng minh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.&lt;\/li&gt;\n&lt;\/ul&gt;\n&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5. Ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa Smart tivi v\u00e0 Internet tivi&lt;\/strong&gt;&lt;\/h2&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Hi\u1ec7n nay, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u1ea7m l\u1eabn gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ecbnh ngh\u0129a Smart tivi v\u00e0 Internet tivi. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa hai d\u00f2ng tivi n\u00e0y l\u00e0:&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Smart tivi:&lt;\/strong&gt;&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb ngo\u00e0i: chu\u1ed9t, b\u00e0n ph\u00edm&lt;\/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;\u0110i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n b\u1eb1ng gi\u1ecdng n\u00f3i, nh\u1eadn d\u1ea1ng b\u1eb1ng khu\u00f4n m\u1eb7t&lt;\/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Kho \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c&lt;\/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t th\u00eam nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng kh\u00e1c t\u00f9y th\u00edch&lt;\/li&gt;\n&lt;\/ul&gt;\n&lt;div class=\&quot;image\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https:\/\/hegka.com\/storage\/image-content\/LZtAUxkK7NTANwv3P5B4QqttwYtse1j9CKwxVop75Seka.jpg\&quot; alt=\&quot;Ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa Smart tivi v\u00e0 Internet tivi\&quot;&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;6. V\u1eady c\u00f3 n\u00ean mua Internet Tivi?&lt;\/strong&gt;&lt;\/h2&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;B\u1ea1n h\u00e3y xem x\u00e9t nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn nh\u1ea5t. N\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n &lt;strong&gt;k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i m\u1ea1ng, xem truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 chi ph\u00ed mua h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf\u00a0&lt;\/strong&gt;th\u00ec Internet tivi l\u00e0 d\u00f2ng tivi ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n.&lt;\/p&gt;\n&lt;div class=\&quot;image\&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=\&quot;https:\/\/hegka.com\/storage\/image-content\/QyuyZZRF2ShNR3nPluGPvCInQjxxp41epCIPJGXmeMc8d.jpg\&quot; alt=\&quot;C\u00f3 n\u00ean mua Internet Tivi?\&quot;&gt;&lt;\/div&gt;\n&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;7. L\u1eddi k\u1ebft&lt;\/strong&gt;&lt;\/h2&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Hi v\u1ecdng qua b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Internet tivi l\u00e0 g\u00ec? V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt n\u00eau tr\u00ean mong r\u1eb1ng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u00edch cho b\u1ea1n!&lt;\/p&gt;\n&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;C\u00e1c d\u00f2ng tivi hi\u1ec7n nay \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 nhu c\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng cao c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng. Internet tivi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ed9 gia \u0111\u00ecnh. V\u1eady Internet tivi l\u00e0 g\u00ec? C\u00f9ng m\u00ecnh kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 ngay nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng th\u00fa v\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Internet tivi trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft sau nh\u00e9!&quot;,&quot;thumb_image&quot;:null,&quot;tags&quot;:[&quot;Internet tivi l\u00e0 g\u00ec?&quot;],&quot;slug&quot;:&quot;internet-tivi-la-gi-nhung-tinh-nang-thu-vi-ban-chua-biet&quot;,&quot;content_share&quot;:null,&quot;image&quot;:&quot;articles\/05-2022\/SAivt4ZjeEtJ8FZzp9fawNiXFuMgN6u0mPqCuVJJ.jpg&quot;,&quot;like&quot;:0,&quot;love&quot;:0,&quot;haha&quot;:0,&quot;wow&quot;:0,&quot;cry&quot;:0,&quot;angry&quot;:0,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;public&quot;,&quot;group_id&quot;:3,&quot;is_active&quot;:1,&quot;created_by&quot;:&quot;USER: #51&quot;,&quot;updated_by&quot;:&quot;ADMIN: #0&quot;,&quot;deleted_by&quot;:null,&quot;created_at&quot;:&quot;2022-05-02T09:12:57.000000Z&quot;,&quot;updated_at&quot;:&quot;2022-05-02T09:12:58.000000Z&quot;,&quot;deleted_at&quot;:null,&quot;parent_id&quot;:null,&quot;user_id&quot;:51,&quot;comment_count&quot;:0,&quot;url&quot;:null,&quot;is_post&quot;:1,&quot;vote&quot;:0,&quot;vote_up&quot;:null,&quot;vote_down&quot;:null,&quot;extension&quot;:&quot;jpg&quot;,&quot;host_share&quot;:null,&quot;link_share&quot;:null,&quot;image_share&quot;:null,&quot;title_share&quot;:null,&quot;reaction&quot;:0,&quot;heart_count&quot;:0,&quot;heart&quot;:null,&quot;width&quot;:0,&quot;height&quot;:0,&quot;ratio&quot;:1,&quot;content_150&quot;:&quot;&lt;p&gt;C\u00e1c d\u00f2ng tivi hi\u1ec7n nay \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 nhu c\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng cao c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng. Internet tivi ch\u00ednh ...&lt;\/p&gt;&quot;,&quot;content_250&quot;:&quot;&lt;p&gt;C\u00e1c d\u00f2ng tivi hi\u1ec7n nay \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 nhu c\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng cao c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng. Internet tivi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ed9 gia \u0111\u00ecnh. V\u1eady Internet tivi l\u00e0 g\u00ec? C\u00f9ng m\u00ecnh kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 ngay nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh n\u0103...&lt;\/p&gt;&quot;,&quot;image_url&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/hegka.com\/storage\/articles\/05-2022\/SAivt4ZjeEtJ8FZzp9fawNiXFuMgN6u0mPqCuVJJ.jpg&quot;,&quot;image_urls&quot;:[],&quot;vote_type&quot;:0}],&quot;banner_left&quot;:&quot;\/images\/left-banner.png&quot;,&quot;banner_right&quot;:&quot;\/images\/right-banner.png&quot;,&quot;banner_top&quot;:&quot;\/images\/top-banner.png&quot;,&quot;background_desktop&quot;:&quot;\/images\/BG.png&quot;},&quot;dataMeta&quot;:{&quot;models&quot;:{&quot;article&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;App\\Models\\Article&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:1505,&quot;relations&quot;:[&quot;user&quot;,&quot;comments&quot;,&quot;group&quot;,&quot;group.translations&quot;,&quot;tagRelationship&quot;],&quot;connection&quot;:&quot;mysql&quot;}}},&quot;checksum&quot;:&quot;2365c4b79e22533fa32d5364b5bf3d8d2ebde9f1de0c2293921122729f6a7817&quot;}}"><!--begin::Post-->
